#  ----------------------------------------------------
#  Only uncomment the following lines if the package
#  creates a subdirectory called cxx_repository for
#  template object files on DEC.  (HINT: try to build on 
#  DEC/CPLANT and see if template-related errors occur)

# -- DEC CXX --
